{"tid":328157,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[斷捨離] 極簡生活","createTime":"2017-07-19T11:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T04:46:57.000Z","uid":118525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fef4fcce5cf444ae0db362075356b3890f0a063f","tid":328157,"uid":118525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"有冇連登仔已經開始極簡生活？可以分享下極簡心得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81968823634aefb4127234f867a24f89ac7a162f","tid":328157,"uid":95097,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"無錢 想唔簡都唔得"},{"pid":"45fa7579e6db437bc26820ef3625b71f864384a4","tid":328157,"uid":18430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"感覺上香港人難啲做到斷捨離，利申想學"},{"pid":"47b329ea130e6f932345ec73df7074188f802982","tid":328157,"uid":61970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:47:51.000Z","msg":"早排好迷極簡主義清走左好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a874ae3395db17e6fc59e32c54a5943e152bd4","tid":328157,"uid":62393,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"現有護膚品要用晒先買<br />\n<br />\n有個list每季只買三樣野<br />\n又有個wish list想買既mark低先<br />\n諗幾日 真係好有需要先買<br />\n但通常十樣有七樣都會幾日後delete<br />\n<br />\n每次買野前都問自己<br />\n「冇呢樣野我會唔會死」<br />\n<br />\n有一個月係淨係俾自己唯一支出係食方面<br />\n想食就食<br />\n但唔想買野番屋企擺<br />\n果個月真係慳左好多"},{"pid":"5044c4404dba04b245255f1fe3b193e4677d6d8c","tid":328157,"uid":6864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"每次買d非消耗品時都會停低諗兩次先<br />\n<br />\n最後發覺好多野原來冇乜用買黎都多餘<br />\n<br />\n掉晒d唔再用嘅野，間屋即時空盪盪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 ： 窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4a2dc2cb6a356b581978154dbe3ba20cfd5d32","tid":328157,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早排好迷極簡主義清走左好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n半年係二手app賣左 成萬蚊野😀<br />\n屋企重係好多野"},{"pid":"691dfff10f705911e98db2cef8efaa37a179ea11","tid":328157,"uid":27961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"簡完D錢去左邊 ??"},{"pid":"7a10ad4702a5efe52e38c7ce1a4365005f427539","tid":328157,"uid":54597,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"(1) 啲野用曬先買，唔好見平，又諗住係消秏品就買定一堆係屋企，廁紙除外。<br />\n(2) 縮減書櫃空間，只留一櫃仔真係好想KEEP既。<br />\n(3) 衫盡量簡化款式<br />\n(4) 鞋按功能只留一對，例如皮鞋一對、行山鞋一對、波鞋一對、拖鞋一對。<br />\n(5) 杯盡掉，飲水用水樽，可以知自己飲左幾多水。留一套4-6隻既杯碟招呼朋友。<br />\n(6) 文具、簿、紙、盡捐。<br />\n(7) 廚房用品最難清，未搞"},{"pid":"c0036da53a8215af3b513cc332bbfff3a023f9c8","tid":328157,"uid":81197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡完D錢去左邊 ??</blockquote><br />\n買新野"},{"pid":"b893ffd1ce563979706df0b69da15e3de68d5aa8","tid":328157,"uid":59211,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"無突登去做<br />\n不過 都咁大個人 有時 旅行 or 人地去完比手信<br />\n其實啲手信擺設都係多鳩餘<br />\n過多幾無又係會 dump<br />\n<br />\n書都係 ，年年書展 都有幾本買左無睇<br />\n最後都係捐<br />\n依幾年慣左 圖書館睇左幾次都真係好鐘意先會買<br />\n<br />\n屋企野， 當你執嘅時候 發覺幾年無掂過 就真係可以dump<br />\n<br />\n再諗深一層 你之後就唔會再買咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ab342db3503faa6efde941c346f05d8b7004b1","tid":328157,"uid":36887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"之前搬屋 同屋企人講不如試下唔好買咁多個櫃裝嘢 <br />\n想試下清走屋企啲嘢 唔好咁多雜物 <br />\n點知佢地一野ban鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一代既生活習慣 又真係好難改變<br />\n可能有一日自己住既時候 就可以實行到呢件事"},{"pid":"00ec84d1b697ca38350d421e926430ef02051991","tid":328157,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係誠品睇左本書講 minimalism 幾有興趣"},{"pid":"dad7823a2169e2c8542f2ed76f354f6521ec948d","tid":328157,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前搬屋 同屋企人講不如試下唔好買咁多個櫃裝嘢 <br />\n想試下清走屋企啲嘢 唔好咁多雜物 <br />\n點知佢地一野ban鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上一代既生活習慣 又真係好難改變<br />\n可能有一日自己住既時候 就可以實行到呢件事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真<br />\n<br />\n多d位擺野你就會亂買<br />\n反而冇地方放仲會諗多兩諗乾脆唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381c27025742467b6af7f096e5f63a87e2d86759","tid":328157,"uid":104454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"less is more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n越大越發覺需要既野唔多<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係心靈富足<br />\n<br />\n仲接觸多左佛學"},{"pid":"6147f98f79cfcc17f2e5a0cfb8eedd8b95c1bbd0","tid":328157,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:54:40.000Z","msg":"窮撚先要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自慰心靈福足"},{"pid":"9f45942ec3dcb7f621e20abe0fb96d9107de578c","tid":328157,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T00:56:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d9d069fdb87773b5969b6ba2497d191e204d2cf","tid":328157,"uid":45290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"你dum 哂啲野叫起手要用咪仲破費"},{"pid":"34578faa6b4f488f96e3fb55053efc84896e861b","tid":328157,"uid":6864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你dum 哂啲野叫起手要用咪仲破費</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇人叫你乜鬼都掉晒佢<br />\n<br />\n只係掉d好耐唔用同埋睇落未來一兩年都唔會用嘅野<br />\n<br />\n同埋掉晒d不必要飾品，懶係有記念價值但收到自己都唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做到咁樣間屋已經少左 1/3 野"},{"pid":"1f90281260562eb63ce562936e58e121ffe06471","tid":328157,"uid":118525,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚先要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自慰心靈福足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁諗就錯了，極簡主義者唔係唔買野，係買真正有需要既野，買野追求有質感，經典款式，可以長期使用，而有質感經典又可以長期用既野，通常都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3975b2bbb2a56e3f77dd20037ba0992033943b1","tid":328157,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"想問啲大型嘢可以點丟？"},{"pid":"9eff6f9d0ab211e47159fe714644af2e9b4b8891","tid":328157,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"由細到大都極簡<br />\n會買啲貴嘅嘢但可以用好耐"},{"pid":"6039c98e6bcd02ed0d9ffdca2b5b76df6bed3197","tid":328157,"uid":6864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮撚先要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自慰心靈福足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁諗就錯了，極簡主義者唔係唔買野，係買真正有需要既野，買野追求有質感，經典款式，可以長期使用，而有質感經典又可以長期用既野，通常都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAggre<br />\n<br />\n貴買平用<br />\n不過原來拉勻十年計買件貴野原來仲慳過買平野又係咁換"}]}